## Educational Use

This project is specifically designed for educational purposes. You are encouraged to:

- Use this project as a learning resource
- Fork and modify for educational assignments
- Share with students and colleagues
- Contribute improvements and educational content

## Attribution

When using this project for educational purposes, please provide attribution:

"Based on TaskFlowPro - Educational .NET Clean Architecture Template"
"Original project: https://github.com/[your-username]/TaskFlowPro"

## Commercial Use

While this project is under MIT license allowing commercial use, it is primarily 
intended for educational purposes. For commercial applications, please consider:

- Reviewing and updating security configurations
- Implementing additional production-ready features
- Conducting thorough security audits
- Adding comprehensive monitoring and logging

## Disclaimer

This educational project may not include all production-ready security measures
and optimizations. Use in production environments at your own discretion and
ensure proper security reviews are conducted.
